Municipal Corporation of Delhi Recruitment 2025 - Walk-in-Interview for 03 Junior Resident Posts
Prasanna / All Government Jobs / Aug 07, 2025, 10:01 IST
 North Delhi Municipal Corporation
 3 Jobs |  Posted On : 07-Aug-2025 |  Delhi |  Salary : 56,100 to 56,100




FOLLOW

The Municipal Corporation of Delhi has announced the official notification for 2025. To fill up the vacancies for 03 Junior Resident Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the BDS can grab this chance and apply for these posts. Here, we include the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for the Municipal Corporation of Delhi Recruitment 2025. Interested and eligible candidates can attend the walk-in interview at the given venue. For more details, visit the official website.




If you are looking for more, here is a list of Government Jobs in 2025 that you can all apply for. Use this link for more jobs in Delhi.

Municipal Corporation of Delhi Recruitment 2025 - Eligibility Criteria
Name of the Posts	No.of Vacancies	Qualification
Junior Resident	03	BDS

Age Limit for the Municipal Corporation of Delhi Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Age Limit: 21 years.
The Maximum Age Limit: 45 years.

Selection Process for the Municipal Corporation of Delhi Recruitment 2025

Interview

Salary Structure for the Municipal Corporation of Delhi Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Salary: Rs. 56,100 /- per month.

Application fee for the Municipal Corporation of Delhi Recruitment 2025

For SC/ ST candidates: Rs. 500 /-
For EWS/ OBC candidates: Rs. 1,000 /-
How to Apply for the Municipal Corporation of Delhi Recruitment 2025
Visit the official website.
Go to the recruitment or career page.
Check for the Junior Resident Jobs 2025.
Read the notification carefully.
Check the eligibility criteria.
If you meet the eligibility criteria.
Download the application form.
Fill out the application form carefully.
Then, attend the interview along with the required documents at the address given below.

Address

 Office of Medical Superintendent, Swami Dayanand Hospital.

Important Dates

Date of Walk-in-Interview	12-08-2025
